/shrug <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub110.ezboard.com/uormethesingingbard.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Orme the Singing Bard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Orcs</span><br> <font color=#000033>(6/11/02 1:44:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=577.topic&index=40>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How many songs can you twist?</span><hr size=1> ** GAWD... I wrote a book **<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Max twist...</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
If we were having a contest, I could get 7 up at once... but it is not a valuable twist.<br>
<br>
Secret to 7 song twisting...<br>
Selos Accelerating Chorus<br>
Amplification<br>
Charm (does amp affect charm length?  I used it in Chardok by accident together and seemed to last longer)<br>
Any regular 3 tick song...<br>
Any regular 3 tick song...<br>
Any regular 3 tick song...<br>
Any regular 3 tick song...<br>
<br>
But that is just to be anal.  Doubt that you'll see that used often.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Twisting 5 Songs</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
There are only 2 battle-worthy ways I know to twist 5 and it isn't a constant 5:<br>
Amplification<br>
3 tick song #1<br>
3 tick song #2<br>
3 tick song #3<br>
3 tick song #4<br>
3 tick song #1<br>
3 tick song #2<br>
3 tick song #3<br>
REPEAT<br>
<br>
Or...<br>
<br>
Charm<br>
3 tick song #1<br>
3 tick song #2<br>
3 tick song #3<br>
3 tick song #4<br>
...say *one dead froglock king, two dead froglock king* (timing to have charm hit JUST as it breaks is tricky, but I've isolated it to counting 2 dead froggies)<br>
Cast Charm again, and repeat.  All your &quot;3 tickers&quot; will fade though well before they're refreshed.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Why 3-4 is the way to go</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
The simple fact is, you cannot do 5 songs unless a song has a longer duration or your going to have breaks in effects.  If there were 5 really uber songs you needed equally bad, then maybe it would make sense... but in most situations I only REALLY need 3, maybe 4....<br>
* Haste/Offense Buff, like Verses of Victory<br>
* Enemy Debuff, like Largo's Absonant<br>
* Stat Buff, like Nillipus March<br>
* Bonus Buff, maybe Katta's or a damage shield.<br>
<br>
My gut feeling is that by trying to get 5 unless a charm situation arises, you will lose a great buff (VoV) for a couple seconds just to have a mediocre buff.<br>
<br>
I always do 4 out of habit.  Depending on the makeup of the group and the enemies, if a particular buff isn't needed, I just through in a pulse of mana.<br>
<br>
After they added the casting bar, twisting 4 became no problem outside the occasional lag spike or missed note.<br>
<br>
Orme Skyveil<br>
Bard of the 52nd Song <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.showPrevMessage?topicID=577.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.showNextMessage?topicID=577.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=577.topic&index=40><img src=http://www.unbeliever.net/images/lanys/postreply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.emailToFriend?topicID=577.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.threadControl?topicID=577.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=577.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=577.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub110.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="eqasylumgeneral">General<option value="eqasylumfrm33">Luclin Info<option value="eqasylumfrm25">Raid Discussions<option value="eqasylumthemerchantsunionbuyselltradeorannounceyourservicesforhire">The Merchant's Union<option value="eqasylumfrm31">Crafts Guild<option value="eqasylumthet